e-a-or-b-equal-to-c/", "solution": null, "score": 1382.760607823, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 2419, "title": "2419. 按位与最大的最长子数组", "slug": "/longest-subarray-with-maximum-bitwise-and/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/longest-subarray-with-maximum-bitwise-and/", "solution": null, "score": 1495.5180147817, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 2871, "title": "2871. 将数组分割成最多数目的子数组", "slug": "/split-array-into-maximum-number-of-subarrays/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/split-array-into-maximum-number-of-subarrays/", "solution": null, "score": 1749.5115037045, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 2401, "title": "2401. 最长优雅子数组", "slug": "/longest-nice-subarray/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/longest-nice-subarray/", "solution": null, "score": 1749.5432375672, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 2680, "title": "2680. 最大或值", "slug": "/maximum-or/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-or/", "solution": null, "score": 1912.1926699881, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 3133, "title": "3133. 数组最后一个元素的最小值", "slug": "/minimum-array-end/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-array-end/", "solution": null, "score": 1934.7806230835, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 3108, "title": "3108. 带权图里旅途的最小代价", "slug": "/minimum-cost-walk-in-weighted-graph/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-cost-walk-in-weighted-graph/", "solution": null, "score": 2108.5054318055, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 3117, "title": "3117. 划分数组得到最小的值之和", "slug": "/minimum-sum-of-values-by-dividing-array/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-sum-of-values-by-dividing-array/", "solution": null, "score": 2735.0909781144, "isPremium": false}, {"id": 3125, "title": "3125. 使得按位与结果为 0 的最大数字", "slug": "/maximum-number-that-makes-result-of-bitwise-and-zero/", "src": "https://leetcode.cn/problems/maximum-number-that-makes-result-of-bitwise-and-zero/", "solution": null, "score": null, "isPremium": true}]}], "problems": []}, {"title": "对于每个右端点 i，计算所有子数组的或值，打印这些或值的分布范围（子数组左端点范围）", "summary": "", "isLeaf": false, "children": [], "problems": []}, {"title": "对于左端点在 [left, right]，右端点为 i 的子数组，OR 值都是 or_val", "summary": "def logTrick(nums: List[int]) -> None:<br>or_left = []  # (子数组或值，最小左端点)<br>for i, x in enumerate(nums):<br>for p in or_left:<br>p[0] |= x  # **根据题目修改**<br>or_left.append([x, i])<br>idx = 1<br>for j in range(1, len(or_left)):<br>if or_left[j][0] != or_left[j - 1][0]:<br>or_left[idx] = or_left[j]<br>idx += 1<br>del or_left[idx:]<br>print(i, x)<br>for k, (or_val, left) in enumerate(or_left):<br>right = or_left[k + 1][1] - 1 if k < len(or_left) - 1 else i<br>print(left, right, or_val)<br>logTrick([4, 2, 1, 5])<br>```<br>```java [sol-Java]<br>class Solution {<br>// 对于每个右端点 i，计算所有子数组的或值，打印这些或值的分布范围（子数组左端点范围）<br>// 时间复杂度 O(nlogU)，其中 U = max(nums)<br>public void logTrick(int[] nums) {<br>List<int[]> orLeft = new ArrayList<>(); // (子数组或值，最小左端点)<br>for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {<br>int x = nums[i];<br>// 计算以 i 为右端点的子数组或值<br>for (int[] p : orLeft) {<br>p[0] |= x; // **根据题目修改**<br>}<br>// x 单独一个数作为子数组<br>orLeft.add(new int[]{x, i});<br>// 原地去重（相同或值只保留最左边的）<br>int m = 1;<br>for (int j = 1; j < orLeft.size(); j++) {<br>if (orLeft.get(j)[0] != orLeft.get(j - 1)[0]) {<br>orLeft.set(m++, orLeft.get(j));<br>}<br>}<br>orLeft.subList(m, orLeft.size()).clear();<br>System.out.println(i + \" \" + x);<br>for (int k = 0; k < m; k++) {<br>int orVal = orLeft.get(k)[0];<br>int left = orLeft.get(k)[1];<br>int right = k < m - 1 ? orLeft.get(k + 1)[1] - 1 : i;<br>// 对于左端点在 [left, right]，右端点为 i 的子数组，OR 值都是 orVal<br>System.out.println(left + \" \" + right + \" \" + orVal);<br>}<br>}<br>}<br>public static void main(String[] args) {<br>new Solution().logTrick(new int[]{4, 2, 1, 5});<br>}<br>}<br>```<br>```cpp [sol-C++]<br>// 对于每个右端点 i，计算所有子数组的或值，打印这些或值的分布范围（子数组左端点范围）<br>// 时间复杂度 O(nlogU)，其中 U = max(nums)<br>void logTrick(vector<int>& nums) {<br>vector<pair<int, int>> or_left; // (子数组或值，最小左端点)<br>for (int i = 0; i < nums.size(); i++) {<br>int x = nums[i];<br>// 计算以 i 为右端点的子数组或值<br>for (auto& [or_val, _] : or_left) {<br>or_val |= x; // **根据题目修改**<br>}<br>// x 单独一个数作为子数组<br>or_left.emplace_back(x, i);<br>// 原地去重（相同或值只保留最左边的）<br>int m = 1;<br>for (int j = 1; j < or_left.size(); j++) {<br>if (or_left[j].first != or_left[j - 1].first) {<br>or_left[m++] = or_left[j];<br>}<br>}<br>or_left.resize(m);<br>cout << i << \" \" << x << endl;<br>for (int k = 0; k < m; k++) {<br>auto [or_val, left] = or_left[k];<br>int right = k + 1 < m ? or_left[k + 1].second - 1 : i;<br>// 对于左端点在 [left, right]，右端点为 i 的子数组，OR 值都是 or_val<br>cout << left << \" \" << right << \" \" << or_val << endl;<br>}<br>}<br>}<br>int main() {<br>vector<int> nums = {4, 2, 1, 5};<br>logTrick(nums);<br>return 0;<br>}<br>```<br>```go [sol-Go]<br>// 对于每个右端点 i，计算所有子数组的或值，打印这些或值的分布范围（子数组左端点范围）<br>// 时间复杂度 O(nlogU)，其中 U = max(nums)<br>func logTrick(nums []int) {<br>type pair struct{ or, left int } // 子数组或值，最小左端点<br>orLeft := []pair{}<br>for i, x := range nums {<br>// 计算以 i 为右端点的子数组或值<br>for j := range orLeft {<br>orLeft[j].or |= x // **根据题目修改**<br>}<br>// x 单独一个数作为子数组<br>orLeft = append(orLeft, pair{x, i})<br>// 原地去重（相同或值只保留最左边的）<br>idx := 1<br>for j := 1; j < len(orLeft); j++ {<br>if orLeft[j].or != orLeft[j-1].or {<br>orLeft[idx] = orLeft[j]<br>idx++<br>}<br>}<br>orLeft = orLeft[:idx]<br>fmt.Println(i, x)<br>for k, p := range orLeft {<br>orVal := p.or<br>left := p.left<br>right := i<br>if k < len(orLeft)-1 {<br>right = orLeft[k+1].left - 1<br>}<br>// 对于左端点在 [left, right]，右端点为 i 的子数组，OR 值都是 orVal<br>fmt.Println(left, right, orVal)<br>}<br>}<br>}<br>func main() {<br>logTrick([]int{4, 2, 1, 5})<br>}<br>```<br>注：下面的部分题目，可以用**滑动窗口+栈**做到更优的 $\\mathcal{O}(n)$ 时间复杂度，见 <a href=\"https://leetcode.cn/problems/find-subarray-with-bitwise-or-closest-to-k/solutions/2798206/li-yong-and-de-xing-zhi-pythonjavacgo-by-gg4d/\">原理讲解（方法二）</a>。<br>", "isLeaf": true, "children": [{"title": "GCD LogTrick", "summary": "", "isLeaf": true, "children": [], "problems": [{"id": 2447, "title": "2447. 最大公因数等于 K 的子数组数目", "slug": "/n